references: Related: CF 203295, CF 203218, CF 203305, CF 203023. Amending: Ord 45382
summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of certain unplatted property in the northeast quarter of Section 10-25-4; Lots 6, 7 and 8, Block 1, Malmo's 1st Addition; the north 55 feet of Lots 1 and 2, Block 15, Lake Union 2nd Addition; and Lot 15, Block 27, Gilman's Additions; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-246 and 17-194, respectively.
